> So I really like the look of the Monza style exhaust, twin tips,  but
> I'm searching for "the one" to go on my upcoming Boston Bob 2L for my
> '73. Anyone got a line on where I can source a good monza style exhaust
> ? I am going to be keeping my stock '73 HE's.
> 
